Title: To the Sepulcher
Description:
Faranell and Velonara already went to the Sepulcher to work on a piece of our plan.

We can hold the wall for now with just a few deathguards and dark rangers, but we need someone who can hit the Scarlets where they are. Preferably without losing more of our own.

Go to the Sepulcher and meet with Velonara. You are the sharpened tip of our poisoned blade.
ObjectivesText: Meet Dark Ranger Velonara in the Sepulcher in Silverpine Forest.
